data.description: **Price Adjusted To Sell!** Stunning traditional with Mid-century Modern feel! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home welcomes you in with gorgeous stained glass features, leading you to the great room with soaring vaulted ceiling, new luxury vinyl plank floor, and cozy wood-burning fireplace with wood mantel - perfect for upcoming celebrations! The kitchen is light, bright, and boasts ample prep and storage space, gorgeous shiplap ceiling, huge walk-in pantry, and matching stainless steel appliance package - any chef's dream! Relax in the luxurious first-level primary suite featuring private access to the enclosed, under air Florida Room, upgraded double vanity, and upgraded walk-in shower. Upstairs, enjoy two more bedrooms, a loft area with gorgeous dark-wood built-ins, and secondary suite. Nestled amongst mature landscaping and located in the highly coveted community of Bryn Mawr, take advantage of all the neighborhood has to offer including clubhouse, playground, park, tennis courts, water views, and community pool! Conveniently located, enjoy ease of access to the airport, Downtown Orlando, the Hourglass district, as well as local shopping, restaurants, and more! This one won't last!
